INSTALLATION:

Linux:
Install ACE using ./configure && make && make install process
Download TinyXml.
Copy contents of build/tinyxml into TinyXml source directory.
Change directory to TinyXml source directory
Run: scons sharedlibrary=1 program=0 install
Change directory to OpenVideo source directory
Make sure ACE.pc and tinyxml.pc are in your PKG_CONFIG_PATH
Run scons
Run scons install
